data.description: Located in Waters Edge on Lake Houston! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath, 2 car garage is situated in a half cul-de-sac. It has an open floor plan. The primary bedroom suite is downstairs with a walk-in closet and a separate soaker tub and shower. The kitchen has 42-inch cabinets, granite countertops, S/S appliances, large walk-in pantry. And it opens to the living room. Amenities include a resort-style pool, a splash pad, a huge recreation center, a fitness center, playgrounds, walking and biking the trails, fishing, and canoeing off the neighborhood pier. Near IAH, Generation Park, Deussen Park, shops, restaurants, and more. Call today for appt!
